title: CDDIS_GNSS_products_clocks_rapid
summary: Satellite and receiver clock products derived from analysis of Global Navigation Satellite System (GNSS) data. These products are the generated by analysis centers in support of the International GNSS Service (IGS) and combined by the IGS analysis coordinator to form the official IGS rapid clock product (daily).
